snippet.title: [EA] Dreamy Duels ~ Tales of Heroes in Gensoukyo - Hearthstone Like with Touhou - Gameplay (PC)
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1477010/Dreamy_Duels__Tales_of_Heroes_in_Gensoukyo/
Dreamy Duels is a card game inspired by Touhou project universe and various other classic card games. In this game, you can craft you own cards with card editor, and use them to engage other players in a diverse card game world.

If you are a dev and want me to delete a video of your game just email me and I'll delet it asap.
contatopobregamer@gmail.com

PC Settings:
GPU - RX 6600 XT Asus Driver: 23.10.1
CPU - RYZEN 5 5600 Stock
RAM: 2X16 3200MHZ
2X SSD 240GB
1X M.2 NVME 512GB
WIN 10
